Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.85,0:01:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴嘛  近江部长
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.89,0:01:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.61,0:01:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到楼上去 剩下的拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:51.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把裙子穿低一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.20,0:01:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.72,0:02:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.24,0:02:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家也快点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.88,0:02:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美星 过来把这个穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在电车里也想这样乱跑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 很高兴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:24.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,县内高中天文联合
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到这么让人激动的组织邀请我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.35,0:02:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和校外的人一起看星星 像这样还是第一次呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.29,0:02:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在大学的时候学生之间也有交流的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.98,0:02:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我高中时还没有涉足天文活动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.94,0:02:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是我第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.97,0:02:43.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.92,0:02:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 果然大家都是相当狂热的星猛者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星猛者？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.19,0:02:52.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我再也等不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么样的人们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:00.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江同学是几年级
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:05.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我来说 没什么特别的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.76,0:03:09.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只希望不要出现新的情敌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.31,0:03:13.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只在以前参加科学馆的天文俱乐部时
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:16.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有和校外的人交流的经历
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 肯定都是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为喜欢星星的人...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好宏伟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.68,0:03:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我们那个什么私立学校不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个要从哪里进去才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.46,0:03:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.60,0:03:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上就来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到你们那去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你们久等...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.90,0:03:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,野木城高中天文部部长 三年级的近江步美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感谢你们的到来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么没什么 初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是部长路万...初次见面！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.23,0:04:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是初次见面？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍荣高中的同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.95,0:04:16.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是副部长樱川 我是二年级的武佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:21.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是宫前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.07,0:04:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是八幡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.02,0:04:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是八日市
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.66,0:04:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是市辺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是京
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.94,0:04:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,8人？！有8个人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 楼上还有人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还还还还有？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:39.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上天台请往这边
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.69,0:04:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 请到里面来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.58,0:05:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们部引以为傲的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:14.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,20cm折射望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.73,0:05:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我是在做梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校里有这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.12,0:05:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从口径上来说跟晴子小姐那副一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.24,0:05:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是几辆车的价格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:29.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要多少万啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长 其他学校的同学也来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,视宁度似乎不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:40.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}シンチレーション:大气折射率不均导致星象的位置摇摆闪烁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气明明这么晴朗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.87,0:05:45.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个单反是什么参数？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.88,0:05:48.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,35mm F1.8 短焦点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 珀耳修斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.69,0:05:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}注:希腊英雄 天文上为英仙座
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.26,0:05:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太萌了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.83,0:05:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天可要好好谈咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星猛者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.13,0:06:00.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 美星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才第一次见面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:03.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.16,0:06:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍荣高中的同学吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.74,0:06:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.76,0:06:10.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是高见女子高中的川村
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是南
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.66,0:06:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的装备还真轻便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.89,0:06:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个也没办法嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.41,0:06:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听好了美星
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.06,0:06:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到处乱跑可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.22,0:06:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 写在手上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:24.96,UP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要太闹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人都在偷偷看你们哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.40,0:06:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们太可爱了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你们喜欢什么星座
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.61,0:06:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快说嘛 快说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一出校门到外面一看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.07,0:06:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是被现实打击了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:43.09,UP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}唯一的装备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.99,0:06:44.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 你们在为器材而烦恼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.54,0:06:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个简单
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做好朋友就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们做好朋友的意思是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字面上的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们这边可不用担心器材
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.98,0:07:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啦 这么快就打成一片了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.97,0:07:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话分组的事情也没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分组？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.43,0:07:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.26,0:07:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人数也增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也想让你们尽快习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:16.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.72,0:07:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先是自由观测
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等到月落
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.28,0:07:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们去测量夜空的亮度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.42,0:07:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮度？！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日程表已经全打印出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请参考这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.61,0:07:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 原来你叫姬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.14,0:07:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人可爱名字也可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:39.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们度过一个美好的夜晚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.25,0:07:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在过祭典一样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.38,0:07:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看啊看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.22,0:07:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星图在电脑上显示出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高科技啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想全都看看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.80,0:07:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请看请看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.27,0:08:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 你太悠闲了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么分组 这么快就被分开了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,江户川
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.05,0:08:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲭人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:18.53,UP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)}无限的住人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.49,0:08:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣鲭人出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.83,0:08:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样要我怎么作战啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.24,0:08:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.40,0:08:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦你们分一下组吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要开始说明了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 莳田同学和我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.67,0:08:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,矢来 这边这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.93,0:08:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明野同学 这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.36,0:08:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 江户川君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我们一年生一起加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:50.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 我和部长呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.52,0:08:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我们一起哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:09:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 县内高中天文部联合秋季观测会开始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么开始说明观测的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.87,0:09:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的观测主题是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.50,0:09:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空的亮度观测
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:15.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家对流星观测已经很熟悉了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都很熟悉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测时要用到的是 我们的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及我们头顶上灿烂的星空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:25.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,区域法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.68,0:09:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某些星星围绕而成的区域中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数出有多少星星能被辨认
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据可以看到的最暗的星等来估算亮度的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在秋天的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这区域就是天马座的大四边形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:43.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次我们要数出这个区域里的星星
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.53,0:09:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据观测的结果
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.02,0:09:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就能知道这个地区的光污染程度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:52.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们今后的活动也有很大帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这么说 这也是个很土的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不只是这次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信和大家一起培养出的经验
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.55,0:10:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有很大用处的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.88,0:10:06.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次苍荣高中的同学们也来参加了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小组的平均数据由我们来统计
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.03,0:10:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请各小组加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.49,0:10:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 直到21点05分月亮落下之前
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进行自由观测
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.83,0:10:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 关灯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,let's go
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.40,0:10:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 天文摄影男子组
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.22,0:10:32.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.33,0:10:34.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍荣高中的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把月亮导入了 请来看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.47,0:10:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是第一次来 给你们优先看了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.81,0:10:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是上弦月 月坑也很清晰哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮 月坑！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.27,0:10:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.46,0:10:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小八
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次有当姐姐的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.54,0:10:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不过她已经二年级了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能看到和上次赏月时正好相反的一侧呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}上集赏月是20号的下弦月
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直想让大家看到月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.01,0:11:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才把观测会推到了新月以后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,9点以后月亮落下后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:15.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会影响观测活动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.63,0:11:20.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 别的地方可没有这么好的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.07,0:11:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,充足的器材 安全的场所
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能参加这样的活动 多亏有高天联
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:26.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}高天联:高中天文部联合
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.44,0:11:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还多亏了近江同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.75,0:11:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢 还靠各位的参加啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:36.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 快看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.78,0:11:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能看到夏季大三角哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.65,0:11:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从它后方逼近过来的黑暗空间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.77,0:11:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是秋季的夜空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像突然开了一个黑色的洞一样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.49,0:11:52.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过近江最喜欢秋天的夜空了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来 刚从东边升起的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:58.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东北方向的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 我查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御夫座的五车二哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,北落师门在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土司空在这个位置的时候 五车二就在这哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这孩子 超便利
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.10,0:12:17.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鹤座的尖端
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边叫什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.60,0:12:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全黑空间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像起风了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.27,0:12:26.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.57,0:12:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能借下收音机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.54,0:12:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了点云嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过既然起风了 云会散掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.67,0:12:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.41,0:12:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 第一次看到认真画气象图的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.90,0:12:45.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍荣高中的人不简单嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级模拟设备
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.21,0:12:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错哦 就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.18,0:12:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把目标映入中央
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.86,0:12:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按下快门
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.22,0:12:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木君
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.24,0:13:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能来下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.10,0:13:07.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.99,0:13:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.18,0:13:14.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还好啦 有点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.26,0:13:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.80,0:13:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.64,0:13:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.21,0:13:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,张嘴就说这种轻薄话的人 最讨厌了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你男朋友不会这么说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.84,0:13:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才没有男朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.45,0:13:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那就是待字闺中了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.03,0:13:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此乃路见受冻的小姐时 绅士之礼节是也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.94,0:13:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想报答的话就和我约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:46.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.37,0:13:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里的 回到楼顶上去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.86,0:13:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.38,0:13:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为是什么事 原来是巡视啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.16,0:13:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 叫你一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来也不想为难他们的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.05,0:14:03.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要有什么万一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.98,0:14:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测会和高天联都会受影响
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.81,0:14:10.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人一多 这种事情也不能不注意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.25,0:14:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.68,0:14:14.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要嘛 很难为情的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.93,0:14:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次苍荣高中也很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.63,0:14:19.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想办个好观测会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看 北落师门
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋天的孤星
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.31,0:14:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年看不到行星 够冷清的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:33.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一看到这副景色 就觉得一年又过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年又一年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你很喜欢秋天的星星哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的部长...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.49,0:14:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 已经转一圈了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.68,0:14:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮马上要落下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.46,0:14:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何必特意跟过来退还衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 有喜欢的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回楼顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.77,0:15:06.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 江户川君就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.59,0:15:13.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续前进吧 我们的天体照片之路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.15,0:15:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的是 小姬的声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.16,0:15:20.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.23,0:15:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分啊 小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.85,0:15:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:40.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想到会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.19,0:15:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回楼顶去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.27,0:15:45.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.00,0:15:46.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a7\fs35\3c&H000099&\fad(0,500)}小姬的视点+小姬的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.14,0:15:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fs35\fad(0,500)}武佐的视点+武佐的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我以为...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没必要道歉的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是武佐同学不对
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我什么都没做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.35,0:16:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是个意外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时候应该是在楼顶的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经参加过几次该熟悉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看你对观测活动很热心 所以我也很信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.69,0:16:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要辜负我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.89,0:16:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也希望你相信我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.85,0:16:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...不知道该怎么应付这种情况
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.72,0:16:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.65,0:16:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之先回楼顶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:37.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.45,0:16:38.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.48,0:16:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好过分啊 小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的衣服就坚持要还回来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说 刚才说的喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.51,0:16:56.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 找到了 部长~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.68,0:16:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月亮沉下去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.47,0:17:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在干吗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.17,0:17:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,步美 发生了什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没有 现在就去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.92,0:17:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莳田同学也冷静下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朔 小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.83,0:17:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 找你们好久
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,观测要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好戏开场了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了去厕所外不能离开楼顶哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空中 空中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.63,0:17:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小姬怎么了 很冷吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.60,0:17:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没没没 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.45,0:17:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 月亮落下后不是一般的暗呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各小组都拿到记录用纸了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.51,0:17:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 对夜空亮度的观测 现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星见妹妹 这里这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.56,0:17:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星见妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:53.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边的小组 让星见妹妹来看星星行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.93,0:17:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.91,0:17:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大八木君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 把事情解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.84,0:18:03.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是用来盖膝盖的 披上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.54,0:18:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说过 要办好观测会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.66,0:18:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 这里的野木城的学生并不全是我们的部员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.25,0:18:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有只参加合宿和观测会之类活动的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.25,0:18:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里的基本都是这种
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像武佐同学 是轻音部的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.07,0:18:24.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正式的部员只有9人而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.67,0:18:26.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.18,0:18:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:31.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想隐瞒的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直被你们说好厉害 就得意了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.02,0:18:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 想向你们炫耀一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带着不是部员的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.74,0:18:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还邀请他校的人来参加 很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没 不会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.66,0:18:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.72,0:18:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想让大家看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是感兴趣 也只有很少的人会去买望远镜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:19:01.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若能自由地使用的话 就会有很多人想看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好 我们有这种自由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.72,0:19:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想让大家都能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.74,0:19:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对苍荣高中的大家也是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.58,0:19:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从一开始就是同样的想法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是说了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.85,0:19:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只要做好朋友就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:29.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是对教会我观星的人的报答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:33.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路万君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,测完亮度之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.70,0:19:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给我们讲神话的故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分乐意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.92,0:19:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要寻找秋天的星座
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从天马座的大四边形开始
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是秋天的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:20:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺着传说中登场的人物一个个看也很美妙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古代的衣索匹亚的王 克甫斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.36,0:20:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}仙王座 Cepheus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的王妃 卡西奥佩娅
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.10,0:20:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}仙后座 Cassiopeia Andromeda
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她炫耀女儿安德洛墨达公主的美貌
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:11.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}仙女座 Andromeda
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.03,0:20:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹恼了海神波塞冬
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安德洛墨达成了献给海怪的祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼看要成为鲸鱼怪兽的食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}鲸鱼座 Cetus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个时刻 骑着飞马来救她的是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.06,0:20:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}天马座 Pegasus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,英雄 珀耳修斯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.55,0:20:31.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}英仙座 Perseus
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:43.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珀耳修斯救出了安德洛墨达
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.27,0:20:46.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人陷入了爱河
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.62,0:20:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸福地生活在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 登场人物一个个出来了 像绘卷一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.80,0:20:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是才看过的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:02.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮度观测区域的附近居然会这么有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太帅了 珀耳修斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我成为你的安德洛墨达吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱川 把M52导入进去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.78,0:21:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a5\fs35}法国天文学家梅西耶制作的星云·星团列表\N被称为梅西耶天体 编号从M1~M110
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.11,0:21:16.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长 我们也...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们也去看我们能看到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和谁一起看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.64,0:21:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看远方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.58,0:21:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们怀着各种各样的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.36,0:21:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凝望着天空
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.30,0:21:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想看的东西 想给别人看的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.18,0:21:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融合各自的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的目光 延伸到宇宙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊 伍岛科学馆的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.35,0:21:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我们以前在同一个天文俱乐部啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:03.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易成了朋友 你却突然退出了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.20,0:22:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.86,0:22:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我是很想来的 但身体受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.03,0:22:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高一的秋天 文化祭的时候看到你好伤心的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.05,0:22:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孤零零的坐在接待台那
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:19.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人那么多有点受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:23.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是今年举办了这么成功的观测会 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.10,0:22:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你不记得我的时候我就在想要怎么惩罚你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.68,0:22:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了星见妹妹 这次观测太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.07,0:22:45.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「居家必备」的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:49.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这之后就要好好准备考试了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.43,0:22:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲惨的3年生
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.37,0:22:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3年...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,考试...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.55,0:22:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,部长你准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当当当当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.74,0:23:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是二年级
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:02.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后见 小姬
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.35,0:23:03.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永别才好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.79,0:23:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 听说你连部员都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统计结果 我们会认真负责地计算出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.21,0:23:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.37,0:23:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,清晨时候多云 没能看到土星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.98,0:23:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,土星啊
